MOTION DOCKET

95-1759. Hunter v. Patterson. Hancock County, No. 5-95-17.

This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Hancock County. Upon consideration of appellant’s expedited motion for order to enjoin trial court action while appeal is pending.

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the expedited motion for order to enjoin trial court action while appeal is pending be, and hereby is, denied.

Douglas, Wright and F.E. Sweeney, JJ., dissent.
